dc_title_s: Addresses Fond du Lac County, WI 2012
dc_description_s: This point data layer represents street addresses for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Fond_du_Lac_Addresses_2012.gdb.[The fire address layer depicts fire address locations in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
